Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:15.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur10\pos(130,593)}#12「直到喜欢上某一点之前」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入9月 第2学期开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忘记君岛孝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我忘记？这是怎么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听懂了吗 明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我警告的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然反而让我更加在意就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 美纱姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然知道君岛孝的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始说明君岛报告No.4的Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 发现君岛报告No.3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:03:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}2 把在种子岛4个推荐地点处拍摄的火箭发射照片上传至「居夫。」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 使用附上GPS Tag的火绳枪 试射1发以上的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4 按下被保管在RoboClinic内的五二郎君的启动开关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五二郎君是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RoboClinic的话也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始 就要在这里组建制GUNVARREL2了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个都能借给我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只要有职员进行监督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有起重机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么空着的话也挺浪费的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可以进行直立组装了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连驱动系统都还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个问题 可以的话倒是想跟Doc商量一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁单…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的事情也包含在内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…由于那个最终话的泄露骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNVARREL的评价一落千丈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要完成制GUNVARREL2 想办法挽回局面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？淳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好跟朋友在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤田外公的外孙女…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我没见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见到他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…谢绝会面？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他不肯见我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？见到Doc了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我昨天去探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明前天淳去的时候就没见到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 他情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看起来虚弱了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止身体方面 心境上也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心境？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算把店关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少见啊 你居然会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有勇气去医院 所以正在这里消沉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和藤田外公的关系本来就挺疏远的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想是不是要退出机器人部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在想这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…真让人为难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你不进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 嘴太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会又插手什么可疑的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你应该得到情报了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:51.05,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}▌NASDA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:51.25,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:51.05,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}全称为日本宇宙开发事业集团（National Space Development Agency of Japan），\N日本政府于1969年设立的以宇宙开发为目的特殊法人，已于2003年10月1日，\N与日本航空宇宙技术研究所(NAL)、宇宙科学研究所(ISAS)合并为宇宙航空研究开发机构(JAXA)。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc原本是NASDA的技术人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NASDA…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是JAXA的前身吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 18年前刚刚开业的RoboClinic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一家面向小孩子的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店前摆放着Doc制造的机器人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记忆犹新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的Doc总是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「机器人可是人类的朋友啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些机器人们现在怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在RoboClinic深处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小淳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个孩子被机器人压倒并因此受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是Doc的外孙女 大德淳和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你好 我的名字是与四郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.28,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是大家的机器人朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呐 跟我握手吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 在想些什么呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做了些什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了些什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 所以淳才对机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算怎么办？小秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说Doc那些机器人的事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由咱们来使它们复活 然后让Doc重新振作起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳也希望Doc打起精神来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你害怕机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想退出机器人部的原因也是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱可没听说这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八汐君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 淳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以会加入机器人部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出于「要是能成为空手道的替代品就好了」的轻率想法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手道虽然水平不好却一直坚持下来了是因为我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然会害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱是不会认可淳退部的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你喜欢上机器人的某一点之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱绝对不会放人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 这是部长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋…秋穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道接有没有电啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电线…被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Doc亲手杀掉的机器人们吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八…八汐君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面修理五二郎君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是无论如何也想修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能修好它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳 能不能来当操纵者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱觉得这个任务只有淳才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 淳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这样应该就OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了吗 好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来就是接上电源…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你…好…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:39.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的…名字…是…与四…郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 已经可以正常说话了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:51.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是…大家…的…机器人…朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小淳？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呐…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:57.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你好 我的名字是与四郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:02.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…机器人…朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小秋 把机器人关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:06.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才…不是什么朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 淳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fr270\pos(722,256)\c&H333431&\bord0\be2\frx6}退部申请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于提交出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点事 先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种关头你那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳的事怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先观察一段时间为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓「难攻不落的话就欲擒故纵」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是恋爱的格言吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊车尾姐姐 我的直拳怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过不要叫我吊车尾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我的踢腿更厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 再做些点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下次再做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平时的你感觉不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时都很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的打算退出机器人部？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然还是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会害怕机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要激励外公也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有我更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得能够激励Doc的只有小淳你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我也一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定还在生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为我是「讨厌的外孙女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc的机器人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电线都被切断了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西…掉在那个仓库里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微考虑一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人可是人类的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我也是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制GUNVARREL1的动画？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很大但是好丑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有武器吗武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家原来是这样看待机器人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能算是在行走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人可是人类的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc一直都很自责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责怪自己以前一厢情愿的认为「机器人是人类的朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过老师却认为那才是一厢情愿的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是豆知识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc变小了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能跟我们一起去RoboClinic一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家店已经关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是毫无利润的店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说这么违心的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该非常喜爱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为咱也最喜欢GUNVARREL了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此无论发生什么事都绝对会完成它 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doc的机器人们倒是都在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你们做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…难道？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是再现了刚开张不久的RoboClinic而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你都做了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要来确认一下我们是不是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出许可已经申请好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又会留下可怕回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…是我让淳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你好 我的名字是与四郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是大家的机器人朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呐 来跟我握手吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呐 来跟我握手吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「藤田外公」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人教会他新的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Doc的外孙女教给「Doc的儿子」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外孙女…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 藤田外公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意原谅我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道歉的人是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 外公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今后不管是与四郎君还是别的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会再次喜欢上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以再次成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点打起精神来 外公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那咱们就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强自己 要养好身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没老到要你来瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么精神看来是没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在制造那个巨型机器人什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等出院了让我看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我确认下它够不够Rock
